animate.y:
Click the button to animate the div with a number of different properties.
// Using multiple unit types within one animation.

$( "#go" ).click(function() {
  $( "#block" ).animate({
    width: "70%",
    opacity: 0.4,
    marginLeft: "0.6in",
    fontSize: "3em",
    borderWidth: "10px"
  }, 1500 );
});

